# valkey-skills CODEOWNERS
#
# Ownership model:
#
# - Default (infrastructure, CI workflows, packaging manifests, skill
#   framework, repo tooling): @valkey-io/skills-maintainers.
# - Project-level governance files (LICENSE / COPYING, CONTRIBUTING,
#   SECURITY, README, CODEOWNERS itself): @valkey-io/core-team.
# - Per-skill content: the domain team closest to the skill, with
#   @valkey-io/skills-maintainers co-reviewing for routing / trigger
#   phrases / CI conformance / cross-file consistency.
#
# Last match wins in GitHub CODEOWNERS, so rules go general -> specific.
# Add a new rule for each new skill as it lands.

# Default: infra, CI, packaging, skill framework.
*                      @valkey-io/skills-maintainers

# Project-level governance.
/COPYING               @valkey-io/core-team
/CONTRIBUTING.md       @valkey-io/core-team
/SECURITY.md           @valkey-io/core-team
/README.md             @valkey-io/core-team
/.github/CODEOWNERS    @valkey-io/core-team

# Per-skill ownership.
/skills/valkey/**      @valkey-io/core-team @valkey-io/skills-maintainers
